just_use main.go

# label: ONE_OFF
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Ingests a Zulip server ("Le Big Mac") into a Gopher production DB ("Le Big
Gopher"). Creates schema via schema.Core if missing so the server doesn't
need to run first. Idempotent — mapping tables track progress so reruns
resume rather than duplicate.

Per memory: the Zulip import is stale as of 2026-04-14 (see
project_db_is_nukable). This tool is a historical artifact rather than a
live pipeline; don't expect it to work without refresh.
